cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper focuses on vision-based positioning in outdoor environments using monocular cameras, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also discusses model compression and update algorithms, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with issues related to large scene changes, which could be relevant to graphics (cs.GR) as well.
